name: QA 541
description:
PCP QA Test No. 541

another variant on ...

535080 - dynamic indoms for pmie, uses sample.dynamic.*

this time, the problem is when the intial instance domain contains

one instance, the pmie expression tree uses the 1:1 operator instead

of the n:1 operator
